{
  "name": "RPlog_The_Chef_s_Special",
  "title": "The Chef's Special",
  "summary": "At Axel Vichten's standing table in the Captain's Table restaurant on Caspar, Axel and Doctor Lynae Cassius dine with the newly thawed Sith Malus, formerly Director, Moff, and Emperor Lorn Rhys, who reveals himself across courses of cold soup and blackened fish. Over whiskey the three spar about the stagnant galaxy, the merits of starting a war, and Malus's stated goal of revenge after twenty years in carbonite stasis, with Lynae probing his true wants and resources while Axel demands to know what is in any arrangement for them. Malus repeatedly elevates Lynae's potential while dismissing Axel as a credit-rich boor, escalating the insults until Axel signals his armed staff and patrons to surround the Sith and reveals he knows exactly who Rhys is. Refusing to be a pawn, Axel stands the room down, leaves the pair to finish their meal, and departs to weigh Malus's fate as Grand Inquisitor of the Imperium. Left alone, Lynae tells Malus to prove his capabilities before she will commit, and he sets a rendezvous seven days hence before masking up and departing.",
